	-----------------------------------------------------
	modes	|	X1	|	X2
	-----------------------------------------------------
	1.0		|	KE	|	1
	1.0		|	1	|	KE
	0.5		|	q^2	|	1
	0.5		|	1	|	q^2
	0.1		|	q	|	q
	----------------------------------------------------
end-hamiltonian-section
end-operator

